article_title: Dispute between former real estate partners in downtown Chattanooga ends quietly

article_metadata.description: Real Estate Partners has settled a lawsuit in which former partner Gina Sakich alleged that secret company retreats, backroom dealings and accounting misappropriations by the firm's other partners were part of a plot to prevent her from selling her share in the business.
